This is my first biggest comment/ review on any social media platforms, whomsoever reading, please bear with me.
Asalu em undi bhayya ee movie lo? Painful comedy, templated scenes, zero twists, below average emotional scenes anthe na .. abbo inka chaala unnai.. usshhhh neerasam vachesindi bhayya first half ke..
Risk teeskoni maree movie ki vella, taking my wife, Dec 31st Night, kind of entered New Year while watching the movie :(
Usually andaru Pros and Cons raastaru.. this movie deserves Cons first ... [if at all Pros unte malli last lo matladukundam]

1. Asalu mana hero ki Solo life gurinchi inspire avvadaniki okka scene ledu, are okka scene anna undali kada bro evarinaina chusi frustate ayi Solo life gurinchi promote cheyadaniki, direct ga college lo speech anta..
2. Friends pelli set aindi ani room vadili vellipoyetappudu aa scenes .. adi comedy na serious scene ah.. basic clarity undadu..
3. Oke okka charecter ki kuda manam connect kamu, except for Rao Ramesh & Vennela Kishore
4. veetiki todu, daridranga epic Ramayanam inspired troublesome scene/ fight/ dialogues ..

5. cheppdam marchipoya.. ammai propose chesthe room lo memories create cheskundam anna chettha dialog.. Desamuduru lo kuda ilanti scene untundi but daaniki kaavalsina background and situaltion untundi movie lo .. ikkada adem undadu..
6. inninti madhalo Vennela Kishore comedy kuda oka point lo irritation teppisthundi [too much of inappropriate Kannada stuffing anipinchindi]
7. Climax lo edo pettalannatu hero ki oka scene, heroine titti vellipoinatlu.. danni justify chesela next scene undakapovadam..
